People, Respondent, v. Tunnicliffe, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. February 18, 1891.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Matham, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements, and motion denied, with $10 costs, without prejudice. See 7 N. Y. Supp. 91.
